Package it.polimi.ingsw.model

Class Cell

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.Cell
public class Cell extends Object
Cell is a class that represents a cell of the board It contains the item that is on the cell and the circumstance of the cell

The circumstance is an int (0, 2, 3, 4) which indicates whether that cell will be used based on the number of players
